# Liabilities Other Financial Liabilities Debt Securities Excluding NCDs Amount

## identifier
de7599

## type
float

## definition
This is the value of debt securities on issue by the reporting party as at the relevant date, excluding those debt securities classified as negotiable certificates of deposit. This item is to be determined in accordance with accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=credit
- name=Liabilities.OtherFinancialLiabilities.DebtSecuritiesExcludingNCDs.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo6.02.06
- period=instant
